videos.description: Nico Mannion fires a nice pass up to the hoop for Josh Green who hauls it in for big alley-oop vs. Gonzaga.

videos.description: Zeke Nnaji is quick on his feet as he jumps up to the rim to clean up his teammates' miss in the second half with authority.
